From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Fedora Hypr Packaging <packager@example.invalid>
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Include mutex for std::mutex

GCC 16 no longer accepts the transitive include that previously exposed
std::mutex. Include the standard header directly.

This matches upstream main after v0.4.6.
---
 src/hyprpicker.hpp | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/hyprpicker.hpp b/src/hyprpicker.hpp
index 94ab520..2751093 100644
--- a/src/hyprpicker.hpp
+++ b/src/hyprpicker.hpp
@@ -1,5 +1,6 @@
 #pragma once
 
+#include <mutex>
 #include "defines.hpp"
 #include "helpers/LayerSurface.hpp"
 #include "helpers/PoolBuffer.hpp"
